_______________________________________________________________________________
"Double Pain"     
        This power allows the psionicist to temporarily alter the pain
        sense in a target.  It does no damage in and of itself, but it
        makes the target so sensitive to pain that NO amount of armor
        will protect it from damage at all.  It lasts a variable amount
 	of time according to the psionicist's guild level.  This is a 
	powerful addition to a psionicists' arsenal and players are 
 	urged not to overlook it simply because it doesn't blast 
        anything by itself.
 
SP Cost:  60		Guild Level:  7		Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  dpain <target>
